    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁阿达尼新进军铜矿，进一步收紧世界矿石供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/billionaire-adani-s-new-copper-foray-to-further-tighten-world-s-ore-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼(Gautam Adani)在印度的铜厂计划明年开工，这将刺激精矿进口大幅增加，进一步收紧冶炼厂所依赖的全球矿石供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/billionaire-adani-s-new-copper-foray-to-further-tighten-world-s-ore-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 05:51:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>押注美联储更积极降息，日元上涨逾 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/yen-gains-more-than-1-on-bets-of-more-aggressive-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员加大了对美联储在 2024 年更大幅度降息的押注，并猜测日本央行退出负利率的时机，日元兑美元汇率上涨逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/yen-gains-more-than-1-on-bets-of-more-aggressive-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与美联储相比，日本央行 2024 年加息仍将保持异常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/boj-set-to-be-outlier-again-as-2024-hike-seen-in-contrast-to-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在长达数十年的战胜通货紧缩的努力中，日本央行已经习惯于成为政策上的局外人。 2024 年情况可能不会有什么不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/boj-set-to-be-outlier-again-as-2024-hike-seen-in-contrast-to-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 03:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
